## Task Creation

This endpoint allows the creation of a new task.

### Request Body

- `title` (string, required): The title of the task.

- `description` (string, required): The description of the task.

- `due_date` (string, required): The due date and time for the task in the format "YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM".

- `status` (string, optional): The status of the task.


Example:

